{"tid":1136779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有線中國組]內地代客吵架服務 最平20蚊一次","createTime":"2019-05-03T08:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T06:54:54.000Z","uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc0b031edcc6de0d382cfb652d430e854a96a50","tid":1136779,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"條片一定要睇，支那人真係奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/868990763442580/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F868990763442580%2F&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjNT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=c054bca6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/868990763442580/</a><br />\n<br />\n有人說，吵架是一門藝術。<br />\n<br />\n如果不想失儀，但心中又真有東西想發洩，卻又不敢出面，怕有失斯文的話，或者有班「罵人高手」可以幫到你。<br />\n<br />\n在淘寶、閑魚等網店，最近多了這些提供代客吵架的服務，視乎要求，價格由20元到100元不等。有些聲稱專業鬧人，邏輯清楚，不會有錯別字。如果加錢用方言都可以，不過用貴州、四川、重慶話就免問。為甚麼？因為無可能鬧贏當地人。<br />\n<br />\n我們說了個理由，落單叫這個人幫我追債，罵一位欠我5000元的同學，對方沒問詳情就答應了。不過只是用文字短訊罵，50元一次。<br />\n<br />\n加上要罵的人的微信後，她便不斷言語轟炸，還說了好多粗俗詆毀的話。我們問她累不累，她說不累；怕不怕舉報，她答無所謂；過程中她一直和買家保持聯繫，發截圖，鬧了半小時後，雖然沒成功催對方還錢，但說她也被人欠債，因此也鬧得很狠，還安慰我叫我不要難過，追不回的錢當買棺材。<br />\n<br />\n至於用語言鬧人的服務就貴好多，對方說收70元一次，問了要罵的對象的姓名和地址後便打去罵。<br />\n<br />\n有賣家說開設這些服務是為了幫人：「我們一直是服務行業，不管是國外還是國內，分擔你的不快是我們的責任嘛。」<br />\n<br />\n至於有甚麼不能罵？他說話如果涉及政治或公權力都不行。<br />\n<br />\n#代客吵架<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"0775098af323aac6d10880f03a9c67ea2ff72366","tid":1136779,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/d53f8794a4c27d1e20d5d17c1ad5ad6edcc43893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fd53f8794a4c27d1e20d5d17c1ad5ad6edcc43893.jpg&h=cbf7b69b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"661d5fbfbc04cb174ab3f7395c1c7649f95dad41","tid":1136779,"uid":9726,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3249773d52cabbd1c084306510c6b4c3bd3111c","tid":1136779,"uid":13013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:03:40.000Z","msg":"用黎收數都好"},{"pid":"157f2498d72c337374bc4da46c7986a5aba1eb27","tid":1136779,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"至於有甚麼不能罵？他說話如果涉及政治或公權力都不行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a78d3ab8d3ef74e5e0486e5ca8d1bd8f0b445d1","tid":1136779,"uid":64953,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:07:30.000Z","msg":"錢多得濟係咪可以請兩個人互鬧？"},{"pid":"99c6f22a63e81c6a65c2dcf7b0729cffbc009dc9","tid":1136779,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"157f2498d72c337374bc4da46c7986a5aba1eb27","tid":1136779,"uid":66242,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:05:51.000Z","msg":"至於有甚麼不能罵？他說話如果涉及政治或公權力都不行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"屌共產黨即刻hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0b60607ee812d54c449bc01a82c89e87dae296","tid":1136779,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0775098af323aac6d10880f03a9c67ea2ff72366","tid":1136779,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T08:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gss0.baidu.com/9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy/zhidao/pic/item/d53f8794a4c27d1e20d5d17c1ad5ad6edcc43893.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss0.baidu.com%2F9fo3dSag_xI4khGko9WTAnF6hhy%2Fzhidao%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fd53f8794a4c27d1e20d5d17c1ad5ad6edcc43893.jpg&h=cb